spec_data.Name: ghc-attoparsec-enumerator
spec_data.Description:
This library allows an Attoparsec parser to receive input incrementally
from an enumerator. This could be used for parsing large files, or
implementing binary network protocols.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 03 Aug 2017 10:51:27 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Pass input from an enumerator to an Attoparsec parser
